    "name": "终结战车",
    "steam_appid": 3211350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到永恒的世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这里玩家将扮演英雄小队的一员，传说中他们战胜了曾经泛滥于世间的死亡之神。而现在，英雄被人们的祈祷唤醒，发现世界正面临着新的威胁。那便是永恒之神在没有死亡之神的世界里控制了一切，让一切事物陷入了停顿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人们被永恒的不变所折磨，于是再次向传说中的英雄求助。这一次英雄们将利用死亡之神的力量，让世界恢复正常。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/61aa3073d6d716af04fd03fd03e1f0c3.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>获取遗物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >神秘商人四处收集拥有力量的遗物。在每场战斗结束后，她就会出现并与你交易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/183f831c6da00d52be6752026c0f4d25.poster.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/183f831c6da00d52be6752026c0f4d25.webm?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/183f831c6da00d52be6752026c0f4d25.mp4?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>使用遗物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将其装备在你的战车上，强化整个队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/61abe910bc5ba950ec532f8dcd0112f6.poster.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/61abe910bc5ba950ec532f8dcd0112f6.webm?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/61abe910bc5ba950ec532f8dcd0112f6.mp4?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>召唤成员</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战斗中可以获得敌人的灵魂碎片，通过消耗能量将它们召唤到自己的车队中，带来更多可能性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/2db57617394f8b7188ba635b8d0fce85.poster.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/2db57617394f8b7188ba635b8d0fce85.webm?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/2db57617394f8b7188ba635b8d0fce85.mp4?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>获取信息</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无所适从？没关系!鼠标停留在想要了解的东西上，它会告诉你需要的信息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/a85dbc8d89332d8e9c4bf323ab173f12.poster.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/a85dbc8d89332d8e9c4bf323ab173f12.webm?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/a85dbc8d89332d8e9c4bf323ab173f12.mp4?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>面对挑战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏，会有三种不同风格的场景和对应的敌人，一共20场普通战斗和3场boss战和最终boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中敌人将如潮水般向你涌来。你需要搭配好遗物与队伍，并不失时机地调整成员的位置或者使用技能，最终取得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/81b710873271e81f9b57d9882961a47a.poster.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/81b710873271e81f9b57d9882961a47a.webm?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/81b710873271e81f9b57d9882961a47a.mp4?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/c57c5e669a5922ef29c4b59cebe8d57e.poster.avif?t=1750644601\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/c57c5e669a5922ef29c4b59cebe8d57e.webm?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211350/extras/c57c5e669a5922ef29c4b59cebe8d57e.mp4?t=1750644601\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
